# Group Auth

## User auth and token [/auth]

### User auth [POST]

+ Request
    + Headers
        ```js
        Content-Type: application/json
        ```
        
    + body
        ```js
        {
            "username": "dan",
            "password": "dan"
        }
        ```

+ Response 200
    + Headers
        ```js
        Content-Type: application/json
        ```

    + body
        ```js
        {
            "type": "bearer",
            "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1aWQiOjEsImlhdCI6MTU1ODk3Njg2MSwiZXhwIjoxNTU5MDYzMjYxfQ.cbaUcANqBYyUmsFKq0PZ9KVPdtLJfxMaG16amQncIug",
            "refreshToken": null
        }
        ```

+ Response 401
    + Headers
        ```js
        Content-Type: application/json
        ```

    + body
        ```js
        [
            {
                "field": "username",
                "message": "Cannot find user with provided username"
            }
        ]
        ```
    
+ Response 401
    + Headers
        ```js
        Content-Type: application/json
        ```

    + body
        ```js
        [
            {
                "field": "password",
                "message": "Invalid user password"
            }
        ]
        ```

### Check token [GET]

+ Request
    + Headers
        ```js
        Content-Type: application/json
        Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1aWQiOjEsImlhdCI6MTU1ODk3Njg2MSwiZXhwIjoxNTU5MDYzMjYxfQ.cbaUcANqBYyUmsFKq0PZ9KVPdtLJfxMaG16amQncIug
        ````

+ Response 200
    + Headers
        ```js
        Content-Type: application/json
        ```

    + body
        ```js
        {
            "id": 1,
            "created_at": "2019-05-27 13:00:59",
            "updated_at": "2019-05-27 13:00:59",
            "username": "dan",
            "email": "danielsilva@email.com"
        }
        ```

+ Response 401
    + Headers
        ```js
        Content-Type: text/html
        ```

